---
title: Gouda Pork Burgers with Caramelized Sriracha Onion & Potato Wedges
description: These bodacious burgers are positively layered with flavor. First, pork patties are infused with an aromatic mix of garlic, onion, and paprika. Then, the cooked burgers are topped with nutty, melty gouda and a tangle of feisty caramelized onions spiked with sriracha and lime. Everything gets tucked into toasty buns spread with creamy garlic-lime sauce and served with a heap of crispy oven fries. Prepare for total taste bud takeover.
